<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

<main>
  <section class="page-hero page-hero-short section-bloop">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Our Story</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about-origin section-bloop">
    <div class="container grid-2 gap-xl">
      <div class="about-img-block">
        <div class="about-img-frame">
          <div class="about-logo-large"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-img-caption">Est. 2026 — Pretoria, South Africa</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">How It Started</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">From the Roastery<br/><em>to your cup.</em></h2>
        <p>Con Leche started the way the best things do — with too much coffee and not enough people to share it with. Our founder, a lifelong cat lover and coffee obsessive, wanted to create a space that felt different. Not sterile. Not pretentious. Just warm.</p>
        <p>The name came naturally. <em>Con leche</em> — with milk — is the simplest expression of coffee made personal. It's coffee the way someone who loves you makes it.</p>
        <p>What started as weekend market pop-ups became a truck, and the truck became something more. A community. A ritual. A Saturday morning you look forward to all week.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-cream about-mission">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Where We're Going</p>
      <h2 class="section-title text-center">Coffee with a <em>bigger heart.</em></h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">🐾</span>
          <h3>The Cat Thing</h3>
          <p>We believe cats make everything better. Our spaces are designed to be cat-friendly — and sometimes the cats show up uninvited, which is exactly as it should be. We partner with local shelters and aim to support cat welfare in Johannesburg.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">🌍</span>
          <h3>Community First</h3>
          <p>We don't want to just sell coffee. We want to be the reason your Saturday has a heartbeat. Run clubs, painting evenings, market days — everything we do is designed to bring people together, not just keep them caffeinated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">☕</span>
          <h3>Craft, Not Shortcuts</h3>
          <p>Every drink is made with intention. We source single-origin beans, we care about extraction, and we train our baristas like they matter — because they do. Our pastries are baked fresh every day. If it's not good enough, it doesn't leave the kitchen.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">🚐</span>
          <h3>We Come to You</h3>
          <p>Our mobile trailer is our heartbeat. From markets to corporate parks to running trails — we believe great coffee should be accessible. No gatekeeping, no bad vibes. Just good drinks, wherever you need them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about-cta">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Start your<br/><em>first chapter.</em></h2>
      <p>Your first QR scan is waiting. Create your account and let every drink count.</p>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start your journey →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
